OL,5, The director of a mine in Burkina Faso 
OL,6, has been found guilty of manslaughter, 
OL,7, following a flooding disaster in April 
OL,8, that killed eight miners.              
OL,10,FHein Frey, of Canadian company Trevali,
OL,11,Fwas fined $3,000 and given a suspended 
OL,12,F24-month prison sentence.              
OL,14,FThe incident caused outrage in the     
OL,15,Fcountry at the time.                   
OL,17,FThe outcome has been met with shock,   
OL,18,Fwith some in Burkina Faso seeing the   
OL,19,Fsentencing as light, given the number  
OL,20,Fof victims.                            
